<quantity box="[857,1017,1681,1703]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.67" metricValueMax="1.76" metricValueMin="1.58" pageId="49" pageNumber="628" unit="mm" value="16.7" valueMax="17.6" valueMin="15.8">15.8–17.6 mm</quantity>
; width across humeri 10.0–11.0 mm. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[940,1009,1708,1729]" pageId="49" pageNumber="628">Color:</emphasis>
Male 
<typeStatus box="[1086,1172,1708,1729]" pageId="49" pageNumber="628">paratype</typeStatus>
with mesometasternal process reddish brown only on apex, metasternum with narrow, longitudinal, reddish brown line at middle. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[457,513,247,268]" pageId="51" pageNumber="630">Legs:</emphasis>
Protibia tridentate in female and male 
<typeStatus box="[420,511,274,295]" pageId="51" pageNumber="630">paratypes</typeStatus>
, with second tooth closer to apex than basal tooth.
</paragraph>
